ends had begun to master it but, for him, the words would not stick together.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His friends\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would not lose track of the letters, nor would they float around the page but he could not differentiate a b from a d, a p from a q and an m from a w. It is a predicament he still faces nearly two decades on in the build-up to theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"the letters\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"a b\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"a p\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"a q\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"a w.\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"a predicament\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly two decades\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had that expectation that one day it would just click but I suddenly realised that wasn't going to happen,\\\" he recalled.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that expectation\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not long after that, he was diagnosed with dyslexia.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dyslexia\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in adult life, reading a book or even a menu is beyond him, and he can only read a few words at a time on a page.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adult life\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"a book\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 903},